text: Andrea Bogorová (born 27 February 2000) is a Slovak footballer who plays as a forward for I. liga žien club Spartak Myjava and the Slovakia women's national team. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Slovak women's footballers Category:Slovakia women's international footballers Category:Spartak Myjava players
